ecu: Support engine diagnosis, natural gas diagnosis, and post-processing diagnosis.

Calibration function: ECU flashing: support Bosch ECU flashing, Nanyue unit pump ECU flashing, Bosch bottom layer flashing, natural gas ECU flashing, Denso ECU flashing, Delphi ECU flashing, Sinotruk ECU flashing, Tian Nake DCU and so on.

Heavy-duty vehicle diagnostic module, supporting multiple communication methods such as Bluetooth, Wi-Fi, USB, etc., can be used with X-431 V+,X-431 PRO3S+ or X-431 PAD III, suitable for 12V and 24V models, covering Cummins, Bosch, Weichai, Yu Diesel, Xichai, Chaochai and other engine software, and Dongfeng Commercial, Foton Commercial, FAW Jiefang, Jiangling, Mercedes-Benz Heavy Truck, Volvo Heavy Truck, Yutong Bus, King Long Bus and more than 100 models worldwide.
support ABS system and dozens of engineering machinery vehicle system diagnosis.
